Using animations is totally OPTIONAL. To do it, set animation effect of the dialog via the data-animation attribute. The value of this attribute which has to be added to the .modal class can be any of the following values:

- slideInOutDown
- slideInOutTop
- slideInOutLeft
- slideInOutRight
- zoomInOut
- rotateInOutDown
- mixInAnimations


Example:-

data-animation="zoomInOut"
